  Version bump

  14 Nov 2011; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> cgal-3.6.1.ebuild,
  cgal-3.7.ebuild:
  QA: cxx conditional was broken, fix it.

  13 Nov 2011; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> cgal-3.6.1.ebuild,
  cgal-3.7.ebuild:
  Convert gmp[-nocxx] to gmp[cxx].

